    "description": "This Peruvian-style chicken is perfectly spiced to go with our take on an aji amarillo-style sauce. You'll roast yellow pepper and blitz it with mayo to create a sweet and vibrant sauce to serve with buttery garlic rice and a refreshing chickpea salad.",
